QuestSimulation class -
    Instance Variables:
        private String name - represents the name of the user's character
        private String class - represents the user's class

    Constructor:
        public QuestSimulation (String userName, String userClass)
            This constructor will create a new QuestSimulation object
            Sets name to userName, sets class to userClass

    Method:
        public String introduction ()
            This method returns the introduction to the quest simulation
            Text customized to user's name and class

        public int wizardDamage ()
            Calculates and returns the damage dealt by 3 wizard attacks using Math.random
                Fireball, Ice breath, 

        public int knightDamage ()
            Calculates and returns the damage dealt by 3 knight attacks using Math.random
                Slash, Parry/Block, Jab

        public int barbarianDamage ()
            Calculates and returns the damage dealt by 3 barbarian attacks using Math.random



QuestRunner.java -

